hopobject.body: Your cash is being counted lithium carbonate buy uk The study – which came out as Prince Charles’s Initiative for Mature Enterprise called for companies not to throw on the scrapheap the 425,000 unemployed men and women aged over 50 – of human resources staff found that just half believe their companies understand the needs of older employees, and even fewer – just 41pc – are making any progress in tapping more mature workers’ full potential.
